				<wikidot:authorName>Gabriel McQueen</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4558836</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I <em>hated</em> this the first time I read it, but, honestly, this is fun. It does start out by reminding me (unfavorably) of a number of pop-culture properties, but it fairly quickly separates itself from the expectations those gave me. Points, too, for not getting bogged down in a too-long list of &quot;oh! I just thought of one more cool example&quot; exploding cars, and the bro-it-up dialogue is better written than what I've come to expect from that type of character. Minus vote changed to a plus, after critical thought.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
